>Description:
When creating a new file, DrScheme refuses to save it into an empty
directory.
>How-To-Repeat:
australia:junk$ mkdir tests
australia:junk$ cd tests
australia:tests$ drscheme -x &

Type 5 into the DrScheme window.
Hit the save button.
type /5.ss in the file dialog.
Click Ok.
Click Ok again...and again...and...
